  <title>Media Remote</title>
  <p>
    To control a media player, start by opening the
    <gui xref="introduction#main-window">Main Window</gui>.
  </p>

  <steps>
    <item>
      <p>
        Open the main window and select a device.
      </p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>
        Open the
        <media style="button" its:translate="no" type="image" src="figures/open-menu-symbolic.svg">
          <gui style="menu" its:translate="yes">Device Menu</gui>
        </media>
        menu and select <gui style="menuitem">Media Remote</gui>.
      </p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>
        Open the dropdown menu to select from the available media players.
      </p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>
        Use the remote to control the media player and volume.
      </p>
    </item>
  </steps>
